Package: causalBatch
Type: Package
Title: Causal Batch Effects
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-01-21
Author: Eric Bridgeford
Maintainer: Eric Bridgeford <ericwb95@gmail.com>
Description: A package for using causal techniques to detect and correct for batch effects in high-dimensional scientific data sets. Also provides a number of useful utilities for generating simulations and balancing covariates across multiple groups/batches of data.
Depends:
  R (>= 4.2.0)
